{"title":"表格和表单","date":"2020-11-06T07:01:35.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年11月6日","L":"2020/11/06","MM-DD":"11-06"},"link":"posts/80afbc07","comments":true,"tags":["HTML5+CSS3"],"categories":["网页设计"],"updated":"2020-11-10T03:37:34.168Z","content":"<h1 id=\"表格\">表格<a href=\"#表格\" title=\"表格\"></a></h1><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106150910.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h2 id=\"lttablegt属性\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code>属性<a href=\"#lttablegt属性\" title=\"&lt;table&gt;属性\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106151158.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><blockquote>\n<p><code>&lt;table&gt;</code>标签属性在实体表格中的表现如下图所示：</p>\n</blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106151416.png\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106151757.png\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /><h2 id=\"lttrgt标签的属性\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签的属性<a href=\"#lttrgt标签的属性\" title=\"&lt;tr&gt;标签的属性\"></a></h2><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>属性</strong></th><th><strong>描述</strong></th><th><strong>常用属性值</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>height</strong></td><td>设置行高度</td><td>像素值</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>align</strong></td><td>设置一行内容的水平对齐方式</td><td>left、center、right</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>valign</strong></td><td>设置一行内容的垂直对齐方式</td><td>top、middle、bottom</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>bgcolor</strong></td><td>设置行背景颜色</td><td>预定义的颜色值、十六进制#RGB、rgb(r,g,b)</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>background</strong></td><td>设置行背景图像</td><td>url地址</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><blockquote>\n<p>注意</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol><li><p><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签无宽度属性width，其宽度取决于表格标签<code>&lt;table&gt;</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>对<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签应用<code>valign</code>属性，用于设置<strong>一行内容的垂直对齐方式</strong>。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>虽然可以对<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签应用background属性，但是在<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签中此属性兼容问题严重。</p>\n</li>\n</ol><h2 id=\"lttdgt标签的属性\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签的属性<a href=\"#lttdgt标签的属性\" title=\"&lt;td&gt;标签的属性\"></a></h2><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>属性名</strong></th><th><strong>含义</strong></th><th><strong>常用属性值</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>width</strong></td><td>设置单元格的宽度</td><td>像素值</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>height</strong></td><td>设置单元格的高度</td><td>像素值</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>align</strong></td><td>设置单元格内容的水平对齐方式</td><td>left、center、right</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>valign</strong></td><td>设置单元格内容的垂直对齐方式</td><td>top、middle、bottom</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>bgcolor</strong></td><td>设置单元格的背景颜色</td><td>预定义的颜色值、十六进制#RGB、rgb(r,g,b)</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>background</strong></td><td>设置单元格的背景图像</td><td>url地址</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>colspan</strong></td><td>设置单元格横跨的列数（用于合并水平方向的单元格）</td><td>正整数</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>rowspan</strong></td><td>设置单元格竖跨的行数（用于合并竖直方向的单元格）</td><td>正整数</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><blockquote>\n<p>注意</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol><li><p>在<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签的属性中，重点掌握colspan和rolspan，其他的属性了解即可，不建议使用，均可用CSS样式属性替代。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>当对某一个<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签应用width属性设置宽度时，该列中的所有单元格均会以设置的宽度显示。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>当对某一个<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签应用height属性设置高度时，该行中的所有单元格均会以设置的高度显示。</p>\n</li>\n</ol><h2 id=\"ltthgt表头标签\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code>表头标签<a href=\"#ltthgt表头标签\" title=\"&lt;th&gt;表头标签\"></a></h2><ul><li>默认加粗居中显示</li>\n</ul><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109083903.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h1 id=\"css控制表格样式\">CSS控制表格样式<a href=\"#css控制表格样式\" title=\"CSS控制表格样式\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"表格边框\">表格边框<a href=\"#表格边框\" title=\"表格边框\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109085536.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><blockquote>\n<p>注意</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol><li><p><code>border-collapse</code>属性的属性值除了<code>collapse</code>（合并）之外，还可以为<code>separate</code>（分离），默认为<code>separate</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>当表格的<code>border-collapse</code>属性设置为<code>collapse</code>时， HTML中设置的<code>cellspacing</code>属性值无效。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>行标签<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>无<code>border</code>样式属性，本书不再做具体的演示，初学者可以自己测试加深理解。</p>\n</li>\n</ol><h2 id=\"单元格边距\">单元格边距<a href=\"#单元格边距\" title=\"单元格边距\"></a></h2><p>设置<strong>单元格内容</strong>与<strong>边框</strong>之间的距离，可以对<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签应用内边距样式属性padding，或对<code>&lt;table&gt;</code>标签应用HTML标签属性<code>cellpadding</code>。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">th</span>,<span class=\"selector-tag\">td</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">border</span>:<span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid <span class=\"number\">#30F</span>;     <span class=\"comment\">/*为单元格单独设置边框*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">padding</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;              <span class=\"comment\">/*为单元格内容与边框设置20px的内边距*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">margin</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;     <span class=\"comment\">/*为单元格与单元格边框之间设置20px的外边距*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"单元格的宽高\">单元格的宽高<a href=\"#单元格的宽高\" title=\"单元格的宽高\"></a></h2><p>对单元格标签<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>应用width和height属性，可以控制单元格<strong>宽度和高度</strong>。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">td</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">Height</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote>\n<p>对同一行中的单元格定义不同的高度，或对同一列中的单元格定义不同的宽度时，最终的宽度或高度<strong>将取其中的较大者</strong>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"表单\">表单<a href=\"#表单\" title=\"表单\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"创建\">创建<a href=\"#创建\" title=\"创建\"></a></h2><p><code>&lt;form&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code>标签用来创建表单。</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109090030.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"url地址\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交方式\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"表单名称\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t各种表单控件</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;form&gt;</code>与<code>&lt;/form&gt;</code>之间的表单控件是由用户自定义的，action、method和name为表单标签<code>&lt;form&gt;</code>的常用属性。</p>\n<h2 id=\"表单控件\">表单控件<a href=\"#表单控件\" title=\"表单控件\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"input控件\">input控件<a href=\"#input控件\" title=\"input控件\"></a></h3><ul><li><p><code>&lt;input /&gt;</code>元素是表单中最常见的元素，网页中常见的<strong>单行文本框</strong>、<strong>单选按钮</strong>、<strong>复选框</strong>等都是通过它定义的。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"控件类型\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p><code>&lt;input /&gt;</code>标签为单标签，<code>type</code>属性为其最基本的属性，其取值有多种，用于指定不同的控件类型。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109090453.png\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /><p><code>hidden</code>对于用户是不可见的，通常用于后台的程序</p>\n<form action=\"#\" method=\"get\">\n请输入邮政编码：<input type=\"text\" name=\"code\" pattern=\"[0-9]{6}\" placeholder=\"请输入6位数的邮政编码\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\"/>\n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入邮政编码：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"code\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"[0-9]&#123;6&#125;\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"请输入6位数的邮政编码\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"textarea控件\">textarea控件<a href=\"#textarea控件\" title=\"textarea控件\"></a></h3><textarea cols=\"每行中的字符数\" rows=\"显示的行数\">\n    文本内容\n</textarea><ul><li><p><code>cols</code>和<code>rows</code>为<code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code>标记的必须属性</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>cols</code>用来定义多行文本输入框<strong>每行中的字符数</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>rows</code>用来定义多行文本输入框显示的<strong>行数</strong>，取值均为<strong>正整数</strong>。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">textarea</span> <span class=\"attr\">cols</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"每行中的字符数\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">rows</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"显示的行数\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t文本内容</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>属性</strong></th><th><strong>属性值</strong></th><th><strong>描述</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>name</strong></td><td>由用户自定义</td><td>控件的名称</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>readonly</strong></td><td>readonly</td><td>该控件内容为只读（不能编辑修改）</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>disabled</strong></td><td>disabled</td><td>第一次加载页面时禁用该控件（显示为灰色）</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><h3 id=\"select控件\">select控件<a href=\"#select控件\" title=\"select控件\"></a></h3><select>\n        <option>选项1</option>\n        <option>选项2</option>\n        <option>选项3</option>\n       ...\n</select><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>选项1<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>选项2<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>选项3<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">       ...</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote>\n<p><code>&lt;select&gt;</code>和<code>&lt;option&gt;</code>标签属性</p>\n</blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201110102646.png\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" /><form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n城区：<br />\n    <select>\n        <optgroup label=\"北京\">\n            <option>东城区</option>\n            <option>西城区</option>\n            <option>朝阳区</option>\n            <option>海淀区</option>\n        </optgroup>\n        <optgroup label=\"上海\">\n            <option>浦东新区</option>\n            <option>徐汇区</option>\n            <option>虹口区</option>\n        </optgroup>\n    </select>\n</form>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"post\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">城区：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span> <span class=\"attr\">label</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"北京\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>东城区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>西城区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>朝阳区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>海淀区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span> <span class=\"attr\">label</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"上海\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>浦东新区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>徐汇区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>虹口区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"html5表单新属性\">HTML5表单新属性<a href=\"#html5表单新属性\" title=\"HTML5表单新属性\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"form属性\">form属性<a href=\"#form属性\" title=\"form属性\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201110103124.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h2 id=\"datalist表单控件既可选择也可填写\">datalist表单控件(既可选择也可填写)<a href=\"#datalist表单控件既可选择也可填写\" title=\"datalist表单控件(既可选择也可填写)\"></a></h2><ul><li><p>网页中的列表通过<code>datalist</code>内的<code>option</code>进行创建。如果用户不希望从列表中选择某项，也可以自行输入其他内容。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>datalist</code>控件通常与<code>input</code>控件配合使用，来定义<code>input</code>的取值。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在使用<code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code>控件时，需要通过<code>id</code>属性为其指定一个唯一的标识，然后为<code>input</code>控件指定<code>list</code>属性，将该属性值设置为<code>datalist</code>对应的id属性值即可。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n请输入用户名：<input type=\"text\" list=\"namelist\"/>\n<datalist id=\"namelist\">\n    <option>admin</option>\n    <option>lucy</option>\n    <option>lily</option>\n</datalist>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\" />        \n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"post\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入用户名：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">list</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"namelist\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">datalist</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"namelist\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>admin<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>lucy<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>lily<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">datalist</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span> /&gt;</span>\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"全新的input控件类型\">全新的input控件类型<a href=\"#全新的input控件类型\" title=\"全新的input控件类型\"></a></h2><p>请输入您的邮箱：<input type=\"email\" name=\"formmail\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请输入您的邮箱：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"email\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"formmail\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请输入个人网址：<input type=\"url\" name=\"user_url\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请输入个人网址：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"url\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_url\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请输入电话号码：<input type=\"tel\" name=\"telphone\" pattern=\"^\\d{11}$\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请输入电话号码：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"tel\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"telphone\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"^\\d&#123;11&#125;$\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入搜索关键词：<input type=\"search\" name=\"searchinfo\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入搜索关键词：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"search\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"searchinfo\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请选取一种颜色：<input type=\"color\" name=\"color1\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请选取一种颜色：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span clas